c: 7
v: 164
t: "Nabiyow cusey: ama marak horta aka maray Sabti ayrot Yallih amri cine maray cagguduk tatre kassiisak sugek Yalli finqisu waah hinnay gibdi digaalah digaalu waa mara macah kassisaanaa? Itte, Sabti ayrót caddok taturak suge mara umaanek waasak suge mari keenil gacisak:umaanek ken kah waasnam sin Rabbih xaqul ken kassisneemih malkit kee Sumaq geynaah usun Yallak meesitaanaah kaal gacaanamkeh iyyaanama keenik iyyen"